<template>
    <swiper
        :slides-per-view="3"
        :space-between="50"
        @swiper="onSwiper"
        @slideChange="onSlideChange"
    >
        <swiper-slide>SLIDE1</swiper-slide>
        <swiper-slide>SLIDE2</swiper-slide>
        <swiper-slide>SLIDE3</swiper-slide>
    </swiper>
    <highlightjs 
        language="js"
        code="
            <swiper
                :slides-per-view=`3`
                :space-between=`50`
                @swiper=`onSwiper`
                @slideChange=`onSlideChange`
            >
                <swiper-slide>SLIDE1</swiper-slide>
                <swiper-slide>SLIDE2</swiper-slide>
                <swiper-slide>SLIDE3</swiper-slide>
            </swiper>
        "
        class="test"
    />
</template>

<script>
import {Swiper, SwiperSlide} from 'swiper/vue';
import 'swiper/css';
import 'highlight.js/lib/common';
import hljsVuePlugin from "@highlightjs/vue-plugin";
export default {
    name: 'SwiperComp',
    components: {
        Swiper,
        SwiperSlide,
        highlightjs: hljsVuePlugin.component
    },
    setUp() {
        const onSwiper = (swiper) => {
            console.log(swiper);
        };

        const onSlideChange = () => {
            console.log('slide change');
        };

        return {
            onSwiper,
            onSlideChange
        }
    }
}
</script>
